{
  "info": {
    "name": "cPorter (local)",
    "description": "cPorter API — local Docker stack (http://localhost:8000).\n\nTwo auth models:\n- CI (API key): Authorization: Bearer cpk_...  — no CSRF, ideal for Postman (deploy/rollback).\n- Admin (session): cookie + X-XSRF-TOKEN — the 'Admin' folder handles CSRF via a pre-request script.\n\nQuick start:\n1. Admin ▸ 1. CSRF, then 2. Login, then 3. Create project, then 4. Create API key\n   (saves {{token}} automatically).\n2. Set {{sha256}} = sha256 of your zip:  sha256sum yourapp.zip\n3. CI ▸ Create deployment (pick the zip file in the 'artifact' field) → 202, saves {{deploymentId}}.\n4. CI ▸ Get deployment → poll until status=success. Deploys are processed by the worker within ~1 min\n   (or run: docker compose exec api php artisan queue:work --stop-when-empty).",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:8000/api/v1" },
    { "key": "slug", "value": "demo" },
    { "key": "token", "value": "" },
    { "key": "sha256", "value": "" },
    { "key": "deploymentId", "value": "" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Health",
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
        "url": "{{baseUrl}}/health"
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "CI (API key)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Whoami",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/whoami"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Create deployment",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const j = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (j.data && j.data.id) { pm.collectionVariables.set('deploymentId', j.data.id); }",
                  "pm.test('accepted', () => pm.expect([200,202]).to.include(pm.response.code));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                { "key": "artifact", "type": "file", "src": null, "description": "Select your .zip artifact" },
                { "key": "sha256", "value": "{{sha256}}", "type": "text", "description": "sha256sum of the zip" },
                { "key": "version", "value": "1.0.0", "type": "text" }
              ]
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/projects/{{slug}}/deployments"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get deployment (poll)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/projects/{{slug}}/deployments/{{deploymentId}}"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Rollback",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{}" },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/projects/{{slug}}/rollback"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Admin (session)",
      "description": "Run in order: 1 → 2 → 3 → 4. The folder pre-request script copies the XSRF-TOKEN cookie into the X-XSRF-TOKEN header for state-changing calls.",
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "prerequest",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "const jar = pm.cookies.jar();",
              "jar.get('localhost', 'XSRF-TOKEN', (err, value) => {",
              "  if (!err && value) {",
              "    pm.request.headers.upsert({ key: 'X-XSRF-TOKEN', value: decodeURIComponent(value) });",
              "  }",
              "});"
            ]
          }
        }
      ],
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1. CSRF cookie",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/csrf"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "2. Login",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@cporter.local\",\n  \"password\": \"password\"\n}" },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "3. Create project",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Demo\",\n  \"base_path\": \"/srv/sites/demo\",\n  \"type\": \"static\"\n}" },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/projects"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "4. Create API key",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const j = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (j.token) { pm.collectionVariables.set('token', j.token); console.log('Saved token to {{token}}'); }"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"ci\",\n  \"scopes\": [\"deploy\", \"read\", \"rollback\"]\n}" },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api-keys"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
